body:
unpopular opinion

everyone saying ‘don’t be mad at dnp about gamingmas!!1!’ is annoying me.

i get that they are doing all this other stuff, but in a way it’s kinda their jobs to upload videos and i think that ending a tradition is a bit sad as some people wait all year for this.

but whenever dan and phil come out with how they aren’t uploading something or they are postponing stuff upsets me because their job is to literally upload stuff onto the internet.

i understand about all the tour stuff but that’s over now, and has been for 3 months, and although they are going to brazil they could always prefilm a bunch of videos before they leave.

i guess this could relate to dan not uploading idk.

i know i’ve enraged a lot of you but it’s my opinion. i’m allowed one too.

summary: no offense but i’m so proud of dan and phil. look what they did this year. they went on a world tour - so many different places,...
body:
no offense but i’m so proud of dan and phil. look what they did this year. they went on a world tour - so many different places, people, shows. they filmed their stage show and edited the entire thing by themselves. they added movie commentary to it. they still did film gaming videos for dapg. they released and created merch. they did liveshows for us. 

and right now they’re on their way to brazil for their movie premiere of their second tour movie, about to do a q&a session, meeting people and trying to livestream parts of this. for us. 

they’ve done so much for us this year. and i’m just so proud of them. and also so damn thankful.
